race.description: D & A Plumbing And Gas Services Handicap (Bm52+)
race.comment: JAYASHREE (5) hasn't been far away in her past couple in stronger grade and looks well placed here on the back of those performances. Slight drop in trip is no issue and she has the speed to offset the sticky gate. Can return to winning ways this time. POLYVANOVA (4) won well two back before finishing just 1L away in a very similar race here 31 days ago. She was only second-up there and has been back to the trials since. Wide draw is a niggle, though she can roll forward and make every post a winner. GONDRINKIN (6) drops right back in trip today which looks a good move, with his last win coming over the mile at Kalgoorlie three starts back. That rating stands out among this field and he has placed at this track and trip before. Can put his best foot forward. HESKET (1) will find this easier today and looks an improver. RIVERCREST MAGIC (11) gets the winkers on again today and is not to be discounted.
